data.description: ** SELLERS NOW OFFERING A $10,000 CREDIT AT CLOSING WITH AN ACCEPTABLE OFFER** Welcome to 200 Glen Forest Drive, located in the quiet, well-established subdivision, Walnut Farms. This beautiful 5-bedroom, and 3-bathroom, grand, brick home has amazing curb appeal! The owners have made several updates to the home which includes, installing a new deck on back porch with trek composite decking and aluminum railing, new light fixtures in the kitchen and removal of blown ceilings in kitchen and den! As you enter, you are greeted by the large foyer, hardwood floors, a dining room, and a formal living room. This flows nicely into the family room that features a wet bar, bright windows providing ample natural sunlight, and a fireplace with built-ins surrounding it.The eat-in kitchen features gorgeous granite counter tops, a large island, window over the sink, an office area, and ample cabinetry! The master boasts a walk-in closet and a stunning ensuite with a soaking tub, standing shower, and separate vanities. The home has 3 more bedrooms and a FROG! The FROG could be the perfect 5th bedroom, office, or playroom- the uses are limitless! Out back the home has a screened in porch, and a deck that overlooks the spacious, fenced-in yard that is surrounded by lush mature trees and landscaping creating privacy. This is the quintessential backyard for kids, pets, and entertaining! This home will not last long in this market, so schedule a showing today, while it is still available!
